{"tid":1076345,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple AirPods 鐳射刻字存政治審查？　中港台禁語不相同","createTime":"2019-03-24T18:49:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-25T13:13:39.000Z","uid":26418,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ac92cd8975a98733fcd29c7b405d24a24b896e53","tid":1076345,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T18:49:29.000Z","msg":"Apple 推出新一代 AirPods ，更加入免費鐳射鐫刻服務，讓用家可以將自己的名字或不同字句刻在充電盒上，讓 AirPods 更加獨一無二。不過，有用家發現，中國、台灣及香港官方網站上的鐳射鐫刻服務原來亦有經過審查。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2019-03-22-16.04.23-694x407.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2019-03-22-16.04.23-694x407.png&h=038938e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/2019-03-22_152507-694x393.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2F2019-03-22_152507-694x393.jpg&h=9da787f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網民發現中國大陸 Apple 的「敏感字詞」數量最多， Unwire 記者以不同敏感字眼測試，發現下面圖中測試的字眼都無法通過。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/2019-03-22_153154-694x480.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2F2019-03-22_153154-694x480.jpg&h=e7a3800f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/2019-03-22_143050-694x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2F2019-03-22_143050-694x400.jpg&h=027fe337&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/2019-03-22_153537-694x472.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2F2019-03-22_153537-694x472.jpg&h=ff6b9c5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/2019-03-22_143540-694x457.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2F2019-03-22_143540-694x457.jpg&h=217105c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲以上圖片取自中國 Apple 官網。<br />\n<br />\n不過值得一提的是，如果以繁體中文輸入部分關鍵字，系統就不再認定有關字眼為「不當詞語」。此外，被視為中國領導人習近平化身的「小熊維尼」，亦可以使用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/2019-03-22_143433-694x453.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2F2019-03-22_143433-694x453.jpg&h=43337567&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲中國 Apple 刻字用繁體中文，某些本來被禁的字詞都可通過。<br />\n<br />\n至於台灣及香港，雖然上面大部分字詞都可以鐫刻，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但「習近平」亦同樣無法使用，</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">而香港更同時無法刻上「一黨專政」字樣。</span></strong>由此看來，兩岸三地的 Apple Store，都有不同的不當字眼列表。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2019-03-22-16.06.26-694x383.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2019-03-22-16.06.26-694x383.png&h=d02a549e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲台灣 Apple 刻字亦有限制<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/2019-03-22_151226-1-694x471.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2F2019-03-22_151226-1-694x471.jpg&h=81fcf121&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2019-03-22-16.02.10-694x442.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2019-03-22-16.02.10-694x442.png&h=f10b83ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>▲以上圖片取自香港 Apple 官網。部份敏感字詞被當成不當字眼，但加入空隔後便可通過</strong></span>"},{"pid":"afc067e96d08ae69953177a4f80aeb82387e6da8","tid":1076345,"uid":26418,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T18:49:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/03/22/apple-airpods-engraving/mobile-music/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F03%2F22%2Fapple-airpods-engraving%2Fmobile-music%2F&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6fCGrV5sAEOTHy2vWGvapoA%3D&h=11b6d830\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/03/22/apple-airpods-engraving/mobile-music/</a>"},{"pid":"bda09885cbc87a08b1f4799f389e9bf36b9f759b","tid":1076345,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T19:24:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efea36c1da8de6d64441c186fc75f5ec4981bb74","tid":1076345,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T19:29:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港台灣都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eba8903baa4cc08b8841be996671cb240ae4564","tid":1076345,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T20:54:02.000Z","msg":"推到更多人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbb782e5532db049ee8a5d395f1f2d146944ee7a","tid":1076345,"uid":1130,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T22:30:48.000Z","msg":"雜種自己都買唔到俾自己"},{"pid":"54d116278c08947a215b36a57641240a392b8067","tid":1076345,"uid":49693,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"fbb782e5532db049ee8a5d395f1f2d146944ee7a","tid":1076345,"uid":1130,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T22:30:48.000Z","msg":"雜種自己都買唔到俾自己"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T22:39:11.000Z","msg":"佢邊洗排呢d平民隊呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgm